1. *Dolazak* na aerodrom je bio planiran u 15 časova. (The *arrival* at the airport was planned at 3 pm.)
2. Ukoliko planirate svoj *dolazak* u grad, obavezno nam javite unapred. (If you are planning your *arrival* in the city, please let us know in advance.)
3. Zbog neplaniranog *dolaska* gostiju, moraćemo da smanjimo količinu hrane. (Due to unexpected *arrival* of guests, we will have to reduce the amount of food.)
4. Razlog mog *dolaska* u Beograd je poslovni sastanak. (The reason for my *arrival* in Belgrade is a business meeting.)
5. Nakon *dolaska* kući, odlučio sam da se odmah istuširam. (After *arriving* home, I decided to take a shower immediately.)
6. Planirali smo *dolazak* u posetu rodbini sledećeg vikenda. (We planned the *arrival* to visit our relatives next weekend.)
7. Kada očekujete *dolazak* novih knjiga u biblioteku? (When do you expect the *arrival* of new books in the library?)
8. Želela bih da izrazim svoju zahvalnost za vaš *dolazak* na venčanje. (I would like to express my gratitude for your *attendance* at the wedding.)
9. Da li ste čuli za novi film koji je upravo u *dolasku* u bioskope? (Have you heard about the new movie that is just *coming* to the cinemas?)
10. *Dolazak* autobusa se kasni zbog saobraćajne gužve. (The *arrival* of the bus is delayed due to traffic jam.)